{"tha-ap545:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap545:0.2":"Bhaddiyavagga ","tha-ap545:0.3":"Sivalittheraapadana ","tha-ap545:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap545:1.2":"sabbadhammesu cakkhuma; ","tha-ap545:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap545:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","tha-ap545:2.1":"Silam tassa asankheyyam, ","tha-ap545:2.2":"samadhi vajirupamo; ","tha-ap545:2.3":"Asankheyyam nanavaram, ","tha-ap545:2.4":"vimutti ca anopama. ","tha-ap545:3.1":"Manujamaranaganam, ","tha-ap545:3.2":"brahmananca samagame; ","tha-ap545:3.3":"Samanabrahmanakinne, ","tha-ap545:3.4":"dhammam desesi nayako. ","tha-ap545:4.1":"Sasavakam mahalabhim, ","tha-ap545:4.2":"punnavantam jutindharam; ","tha-ap545:4.3":"Thapesi etadaggamhi, ","tha-ap545:4.4":"parisasu visarado. ","tha-ap545:5.1":"Tadaham khattiyo asim, ","tha-ap545:5.2":"nagare hamsasavhaye; ","tha-ap545:5.3":"Sutva jinassa tam vakyam, ","tha-ap545:5.4":"savakassa gunam bahum. ","tha-ap545:6.1":"Nimantayitva sattaham, ","tha-ap545:6.2":"bhojayitva sasavakam; ","tha-ap545:6.3":"Mahadanam daditvana, ","tha-ap545:6.4":"tam thanamabhipatthayim. ","tha-ap545:7.1":"Tada mam vinatam pade, ","tha-ap545:7.2":"disvana purisasabho; ","tha-ap545:7.3":"Sarena mahata viro, ","tha-ap545:7.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","tha-ap545:8.1":"‘Tato jinassa vacanam, ","tha-ap545:8.2":"sotukama mahajana; ","tha-ap545:8.3":"Devadanavagandhabba, ","tha-ap545:8.4":"brahmano ca mahiddhika’. ","tha-ap545:9.1":"Samanabrahmana ceva, ","tha-ap545:9.2":"namassimsu katanjali; ","tha-ap545:9.3":"‘Namo te purisajanna, ","tha-ap545:9.4":"namo te purisuttama. ","tha-ap545:10.1":"Khattiyena mahadanam, ","tha-ap545:10.2":"dinnam sattahikampi vo; ","tha-ap545:10.3":"Sotukama phalam tassa, ","tha-ap545:10.4":"byakarohi mahamune’. ","tha-ap545:11.1":"Tato avoca bhagava, ","tha-ap545:11.2":"‘sunatha mama bhasitam; ","tha-ap545:11.3":"Appameyyamhi buddhamhi, ","tha-ap545:11.4":"sasanghamhi patitthita. ","tha-ap545:12.1":"Dakkhina taya ko vatta, ","tha-ap545:12.2":"appameyyaphala hi sa; ","tha-ap545:12.3":"Api ce sa mahabhogo, ","tha-ap545:12.4":"thanam pattheti uttamam. ","tha-ap545:13.1":"Labhi vipulalabhanam, ","tha-ap545:13.2":"yatha bhikkhu sudassano; ","tha-ap545:13.3":"Tathahampi bhaveyyanti, ","tha-ap545:13.4":"lacchase tam anagate. ","tha-ap545:14.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap545:14.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap545:14.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap545:14.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap545:15.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap545:15.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap545:15.3":"Sivali nama namena, ","tha-ap545:15.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap545:16.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap545:16.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap545:16.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap545:16.4":"tavatimsupago aham. ","tha-ap545:17.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap545:17.2":"vipassi lokanayako; ","tha-ap545:17.3":"Uppajji carudassano, ","tha-ap545:17.4":"sabbadhammavipassako. ","tha-ap545:18.1":"Tadaham bandhumatiyam, ","tha-ap545:18.2":"kulassannatarassa ca; ","tha-ap545:18.3":"Dayito passito ceva, ","tha-ap545:18.4":"asim kammantavavato. ","tha-ap545:19.1":"Tada annataro pugo, ","tha-ap545:19.2":"vipassissa mahesino; ","tha-ap545:19.3":"Parivesam akarayi, ","tha-ap545:19.4":"mahantamativissutam. ","tha-ap545:20.1":"Nitthite ca mahadane, ","tha-ap545:20.2":"dadum khajjakasanhitam; ","tha-ap545:20.3":"Navam dadhim madhunceva, ","tha-ap545:20.4":"vicinam neva addasum. ","tha-ap545:21.1":"Tadaham tam gahetvana, ","tha-ap545:21.2":"navam dadhim madhumpi ca; ","tha-ap545:21.3":"Kammassamigharam gacchim, ","tha-ap545:21.4":"tamesanta mamaddasum. ","tha-ap545:22.1":"Sahassamapi datvana, ","tha-ap545:22.2":"nalabhimsu ca tam dvayam; ","tha-ap545:22.3":"Tatoham evam cintesim, ","tha-ap545:22.4":"‘netam hessati orakam. ","tha-ap545:23.1":"Yatha ime jana sabbe, ","tha-ap545:23.2":"sakkaronti tathagatam; ","tha-ap545:23.3":"Ahampi karam kassami, ","tha-ap545:23.4":"sasanghe lokanayake’. ","tha-ap545:24.1":"Tadahamevam cintetva, ","tha-ap545:24.2":"dadhim madhunca ekato; ","tha-ap545:24.3":"Madditva lokanathassa, ","tha-ap545:24.4":"sasanghassa adasaham. ","tha-ap545:25.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap545:25.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap545:25.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap545:25.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap545:26.1":"Punaham baranasiyam, ","tha-ap545:26.2":"raja hutva mahayaso; ","tha-ap545:26.3":"Sattukassa tada duttho, ","tha-ap545:26.4":"dvararodhamakarayim. ","tha-ap545:27.1":"Tada tapassino ruddha, ","tha-ap545:27.2":"ekaham rakkhita ahum; ","tha-ap545:27.3":"Tato tassa vipakena, ","tha-ap545:27.4":"papatim nirayam bhusam. ","tha-ap545:28.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","tha-ap545:28.2":"jatoham koliye pure; ","tha-ap545:28.3":"Suppavasa ca me mata, ","tha-ap545:28.4":"mahali licchavi pita. ","tha-ap545:29.1":"Khattiye punnakammena, ","tha-ap545:29.2":"dvararodhassa vahasa; ","tha-ap545:29.3":"Satta vassani nivasim, ","tha-ap545:29.4":"matukucchimhi dukkhito. ","tha-ap545:30.1":"Sattaham dvaramulhoham, ","tha-ap545:30.2":"mahadukkhasamappito; ","tha-ap545:30.3":"Mata me chandadanena, ","tha-ap545:30.4":"evam asi sudukkhita. ","tha-ap545:31.1":"Suvatthitoham nikkhanto, ","tha-ap545:31.2":"buddhena anukampito; ","tha-ap545:31.3":"Nikkhantadivaseyeva, ","tha-ap545:31.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap545:32.1":"Upajjha sariputto me, ","tha-ap545:32.2":"moggallano mahiddhiko; ","tha-ap545:32.3":"Kese oropayanto me, ","tha-ap545:32.4":"anusasi mahamati. ","tha-ap545:33.1":"Kesesu chijjamanesu, ","tha-ap545:33.2":"arahattamapapunim; ","tha-ap545:33.3":"Deva naga manussa ca, ","tha-ap545:33.4":"paccaye upanenti me. ","tha-ap545:34.1":"Padumuttaranathanca, ","tha-ap545:34.2":"vipassinca vinayakam; ","tha-ap545:34.3":"Yam pujayim pamudito, ","tha-ap545:34.4":"paccayehi visesato. ","tha-ap545:35.1":"Tato tesam visesena, ","tha-ap545:35.2":"kammanam vipuluttamam; ","tha-ap545:35.3":"Labham labhami sabbattha, ","tha-ap545:35.4":"vane game jale thale. ","tha-ap545:36.1":"Revatam dassanatthaya, ","tha-ap545:36.2":"yada yati vinayako; ","tha-ap545:36.3":"Timsabhikkhusahassehi, ","tha-ap545:36.4":"saha lokagganayako. ","tha-ap545:37.1":"Tada devopanitehi, ","tha-ap545:37.2":"mamatthaya mahamati; ","tha-ap545:37.3":"Paccayehi mahaviro, ","tha-ap545:37.4":"sasangho lokanayako. ","tha-ap545:38.1":"Upatthito maya buddho, ","tha-ap545:38.2":"gantva revatamaddasa; ","tha-ap545:38.3":"Tato jetavanam gantva, ","tha-ap545:38.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap545:39.1":"‘Labhinam sivali aggo, ","tha-ap545:39.2":"mama sissesu bhikkhavo’; ","tha-ap545:39.3":"Sabbalokahito sattha, ","tha-ap545:39.4":"kittayi parisasu mam. ","tha-ap545:40.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap545:40.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap545:40.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap545:41.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap545:41.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap545:41.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap545:42.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap545:42.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap545:42.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap545:43.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sivalithero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap545:44.1":"Sivalittherassapadanam tatiyam. "}